\pard\f0\fs28 Rhizome dictyostelic, with clathrate scales. Petiole with 2 vascular strands, often fusing to form a single ×-shaped strand. Sori superficial, borne along one or both sides of the fertile veins; spores bilateral.
\par

\par

\pard\f0\fs28\qc {\b 1.               Asplenium}                  L.
